resources.string:
	2fit is fitness app which allows you to achieve great results, within a short period of time. In addition, 2fit is an extensive database of exercises for every muscle, with a detailed description and video for each exercise. 

-Exercises with video support for every workout;


-A list of the most effective workouts for every muscle group;


-Text instruction with pictures for each exercise;


-Exercise database with new exercises added after each update;


-Pedometer to count steps while walking;


-Calories counter to see how calories you have burnt;
